title: Autodesk 3DS Max 2008
description:
Autodesk 3DS Max 2008
---------------------

1. Install 3DS Max 2008 with the components you want.

2. First time you start the program, it will ask for activation.

3. Choose to activate the product.

4. Type in a serial. Use one of these:
   666-20082008
   646-20082008
   653-12344321
   648-98766789

5. Click &#039;Enter activation code&#039;.

6. Run the keygen that fits - 32bit or 64bit.

7. Copy-Paste the given request code into the keygen.

8. Copy-Paste the activation code from keygen.

9. Click Next.

10. Enjoy!


/Ubehage
